name: Georgepnk Walkerpnk Bushpnk
description: Prior to getting married, Bush struggled with multiple episodes of alcohol abuse.[24] In one instance on September 4, 1976, he was pulled over near his family's summer home in Kennebunkport, Maine, for driving under the influence of alcohol. He was cited for DUI, fined $150, and got his Maine driver's license briefly suspended.[25] Bush said his wife has had a stabilizing effect on his life,[21] and he attributes her influence to his 1986 decision to give up alcohol.
